msgid "FFmpeg"
msgstr "FFmpeg"

#: ../../importing_and_assets_management/capturing.rst:98
msgid ""
"I believe this captures video from an installed Web Cam using *Video4Linux2*."
msgstr "我相信这会调用 *Video4Linux2* 从已安装的网络摄像头录制视频。"

